{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM05_ST4_540.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x20,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Unexpected load confirmed.<CR>Action...ceased."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Y-You're not Nio, are you? Who are you?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Why do you look like Nio?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Nio? This specimen's name?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Yes. She's my sister.<CR>Please give Nio back to me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "That, I cannot allow.<CR>I am the keeper of \"this.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Then stop keeping her.<CR>And don't call Nio \"this\"!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0x1,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "All of my actions have been authorized."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0x1,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Any interference will be eliminated by any means necessary."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0x1,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Further hinderances will not be tolerated. Alchemist, this is your only warning."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7b,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "No matter what you say, I won't back down! Give me back my sister!!!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Ah! Wait...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Hmph. That's quite a considerable tantrum."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xcc,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I'm throwing a tantrum, too! Treating...Nio like...! *sob*"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Don't cry... I can't deal with crying women."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Sorry, I got upset. But, I don't know what I'm supposed to do..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I don't know what that thing was..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "But it's going too far for something that was created by human hands."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xcd,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Plus, treating Nio like a thing...<CR>*sob* *sob*"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x91,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Ugh, don't fret."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x93,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I won't say that there's no benefit to crying, but is that really what you should be doing right now?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xce,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Sorry, I'm sudch a grybaby..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "If you want to cry, cry all you want after you save your sister."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Not all alchemists use their skills for the greater good."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Or maybe it's... Never mind, that's only a hypothesis."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Regardless, if we can locate where it is, we can come up with a way to deal with it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Do you have any ideas?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xcf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Ideas...? They aren't directly related, but a few things do come to mind..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Then let's meet at the edge of town and go from there."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x15,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Come find me after you've calmed yourself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "(That's right. Now's not the time to cry. I need to hurry and find Nio.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You got the book: Forbidden Nocturne."
        }
    ]
}